Mark Moreno

Mark Moreno

Huntington Beach CA

Hey friendo.. thanks for stopping by, hope you like my vibe. I play what I like and I got a big appetite. Some days I feel like dropping hard hitting house music or some 90s throwbacks... Some days its reggae all day.. guess thats what living at the beach and surfing does to you... Hit that like button and lets become best friends! https://www.youtube.com/@markmorenousa/videos www.markmorenousa.com https://music.apple.com/us/artist/mark-moreno/693688108 https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/dj-mark-moreno/id1572952012
